<li id="cite_note-dorminandshrine-22">^ <a href="#cite_ref-dorminandshrine_22-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-dorminandshrine_22-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-dorminandshrine_22-2" title=""><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <b>Emon (narrating):</b> That place... began from the resonance of intersecting points... They are memories replaced by ens and naught and etched into stone. Blood, young sprouts, sky—and the one with the ability to control beings created from light... In that world, it is said that if one should wish it one can bring back the souls of the dead... ...But to trespass upon that land is strictly forbidden... <cite>Sony Computer Entertainment. <i>Shadow of the Colossus</i>.  (Sony Computer Entertainment). PlayStation 2. <span style="color:#555;">(in English)</span>. (2005-10-18)</cite></li>
