<li id="cite_note-dengeki-39"><b><a href="#cite_ref-dengeki_39-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://dol.dengeki.com/soft/recommend/wander/" class="external text" title="http://dol.dengeki.com/soft/recommend/wander/" rel="nofollow">"Interview Wander to Kyozō"</a> (in Japanese). <i><a href="http://dol.dengeki.com/index.html" class="external text" title="http://dol.dengeki.com/index.html" rel="nofollow">Dengeki Online.com</a></i>. 2005<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://dol.dengeki.com/soft/recommend/wander/" class="external free" title="http://dol.dengeki.com/soft/recommend/wander/" rel="nofollow">http://dol.dengeki.com/soft/recommend/wander/</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on March 12 2008</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Interview+Wander+to+Kyoz%C5%8D&amp;rft.atitle=%5Bhttp%3A%2F%2Fdol.dengeki.com%2Findex.html+Dengeki+Online.com%5D&amp;rft.date=2005&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fdol.dengeki.com%2Fsoft%2Frecommend%2Fwander%2F&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Shadow_of_the_Colossus"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span> Translation of paragraph 1:<br />
<b>Ueda Fumihito</b>: <i>In the first stages of development, "Wander to Kyozō" was called "Nico," short for "Next Ico." The idea for our new game was to use what we had learned in "Ico" and come up with something new. However, "Nico" was nothing more than a temporary project name and it was clear from the beginning that the title would change</i>.</li>
<li id="cite_note-makingcolossalgames-40">^ <a href="#cite_ref-makingcolossalgames_40-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-makingcolossalgames_40-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-makingcolossalgames_40-2" title=""><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-makingcolossalgames_40-3" title=""><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFKosak.2C_Dave_.22Fargo.222006">Kosak, Dave "Fargo" (2006). <a href="http://ps2.gamespy.com/playstation-2/ico-ii/688379p2.html" class="external text" title="http://ps2.gamespy.com/playstation-2/ico-ii/688379p2.html" rel="nofollow">"Making Colossal Games"</a>. <i><a href="http://ps2.gamespy.com/" class="external text" title="http://ps2.gamespy.com/" rel="nofollow">GameSpy</a></i><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://ps2.gamespy.com/playstation-2/ico-ii/688379p2.html" class="external free" title="http://ps2.gamespy.com/playstation-2/ico-ii/688379p2.html" rel="nofollow">http://ps2.gamespy.com/playstation-2/ico-ii/688379p2.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on July 18 2006</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Making+Colossal+Games&amp;rft.atitle=%5Bhttp%3A%2F%2Fps2.gamespy.com%2F+GameSpy%5D&amp;rft.aulast=Kosak%2C+Dave+%22Fargo%22&amp;rft.au=Kosak%2C+Dave+%22Fargo%22&amp;rft.date=2006&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fps2.gamespy.com%2Fplaystation-2%2Fico-ii%2F688379p2.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Shadow_of_the_Colossus"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
